      '  • בלתי מזוהה (use ONLY when text is gibberish — confidence must be < 0.3)\n\n' +
      'CONFIDENCE GUIDE:\n' +
      '  0.95-1.00 → exact match to known vendor (e.g. "shufersal", "wolt", "ארומה")\n' +
